FRED SQLAlchemy interfaces.

finagg.fred.sql.metadata

The metadata associated with all SQL tables defined in this module.

finagg.fred.sql.series

SQL table for storing raw data as managed by finagg.fred.feat.series (an alias for finagg.fred.feat.Series).

finagg.fred.sql.economic

SQL table for storing refined data as managed by finagg.fred.feat.economic (an alias for finagg.fred.feat.Economic).
